{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1681-07a_281"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Berger Fleuriste, à la Nymphe des Bruyeres"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juillet 1681 (première partie) [tome 7], p. 281-288."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous ay déja parlé bien des fois du Berger Fleuriste, & la délicatesse de son esprit vous est connuë par plusieurs de ses Ouvrages qui ont embelly mes Lettres. Ainsi je ne sçaurois mieux vous préparer à une lecture agreable, qu’en vous disant que le Billet que vous allez voir est de sa façon. Il accompagnoit un Présent de Fleurs, envoyé à une Belle le jour de sa Feste."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "LE BERGER FLEURISTE,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "A la Nymphe des Bruyeres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne vous envoyer point de Fleurs le jour de vostre Feste, belle Nymphe, & vous écrire pour excuse que les plus brillantes des Parterres perdent leur lustre aupres de celles de vostre teint ; qu’à vostre approche les plus blanches semblent devenir pâles, & les plus vermeilles rougir de honte, & que deux Soleils feroient bientost mourir ce qu’un seul fait naître,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Ce seroit faire le Badin,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vous donner d’assez mauvaise grace,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Pour de belles Fleurs de Jardin,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Les plus communes du Parnasse."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "L’amitié tendre, aussi-bien que l’amour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous en doit, du moins en ce jour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Présenter de plus naturelles."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce tribut appartient au nom que vous portez ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " Et s’il se paye aux moindres Belles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous, que l’on voit briller de cent rares beautez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous laisse à penser, si vous le méritez."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne vous en offrir d’ailleurs qu’en petite quantité, & vous mander pour raison de cette épargne,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous en auriez eu davantage."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "  Mais quoy, dés le matin"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Abeilles ont mis le Parterre au pillage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Et s’en vont avec leur butin."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Il leur faut pardonner aujourd’huy ce ravage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Elles l’ont fait à bonne fin."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Zéphirs mes amis, m’ont dit que cette Queste"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Estoit pour celébrer, par un fameux Festin,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "  Ce jour de vostre Feste."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous connois, belle Nymphe. Vous seriez d’humeur à ne croire ny les Zéphirs, ny leur Truchement, & l’on courreroit risque de ne passer aupres de vous que pour un Conteur de Nouvelles faites à plaisir L’inconvénient m’a paru fâcheux, & pour l’éviter, j’ay fait amasser des Fleurs, & vous en envoye trois Corbeilles toutes pleines."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Céladon, de ma part, vous les va présenter,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "  Et j’ose me flater"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Qu’elles vous seront agreables."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Elles parfument l’air d’une charmante odeur ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "L’innocence & l’amour brillent dans leur couleur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Il n’en est point de plus aimables."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Roses & les Lys n’ont point tant de beautez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce sont pour les Autels des ornemens passables ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais voicy ce qu’il faut pour les Divinitez."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Fleurs d’Orange & de Grénade, Jasmin de France & d’Espagne, & Oeillets de toutes les sortes. Je n’ay pas voulu les mettre en Bouquets, ç’auroit esté entreprendre mal-à-propos sur cet esprit de discernement & d’invention dont vous estes pleine jusqu’au bout des doigts, & qui rend tous vos Ouvrages si beaux, qu’on n’en voit point de mieux travaillez que ceux qui sortent de vos mains."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " C’est donc à vostre adresse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " A faire valloir leur richesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "A ménager leur rang, leur éclat, leur douceur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et puis à les placer sur vostre aimable cœur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est là que vous allez finir vos destinées,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Fleurs trois fois fortunées ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et c’est là qu’un Amant mettroit tout son bonheur"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "  A finir ses années."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour moy, belle Nymphe, bien que je ne sois qu’au nombre de vos Amis, sans mentir, en cette rencontre, si je l’ose dire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je suis du sentiment de vos Adorateurs."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Je voudrois bien avoir le destin de mes Fleurs."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Tout iroit à me satisfaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous me regarderiez comme un joly présent,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " J’aurois le bonheur de vous plaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et je mourrois en vous plaisant."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Est-il rien de plus doux, & de plus innocent ?"}]}]}]}]}]}